headline: MangoBoost Sets New Benchmark with Record-Breaking DPU-Based AI Training Storage Solution in MLPerf Storage v2.0
summary: BELLEVUE, Wash., August 04, 2025--MangoBoost, a provider of cutting-edge system solutions for maximizing compute efficiency and scalability, has delivered record-breaking performance in the latest MLPerf Storage v2.0 with its Mango StorageBoost™ solution. This achievement marks a major milestone for DPU-accelerated NVMe/TCP storage systems, showcasing industry-leading performance, efficiency, and scalability for AI training workloads.

headline: No Jitters, Just Clarity: Everyday Dose Now at Target Nationwide
summary: Everyday Dose, the coffee that does more, has officially launched in over 1500 Target stores nationwide and online at Target.com. This major retail expansion marks a significant milestone for the brand as it brings focus, clarity, and calm energy, without the crash or anxiety that comes with traditional coffee, to a broader audience seeking a better way to start their day.

headline: Javvy Coffee Launches Its Viral Protein Coffee at Select Target Stores Nationwide
summary: The internet's favorite brew, Javvy Coffee, is officially expanding to Target shelves nationwide! With the growing demand for healthier coffee alternatives, Javvy Coffee is stepping up with a better-for-you, protein-packed option that delivers on both taste and convenience. Starting August 3rd, Javvy Protein Coffee will be available in the coffee aisle at select Target locations and on Target.com.

headline: Registration for People of Play™'s 2025 Young Inventor Challenge® Opens Today
summary: People of Play™ (POP), a leading community of toy industry professionals, proudly announces the 20th annual Young Inventor Challenge® (YIC) International Championship. Registration is open now through October 26 for children ages 6-18 to submit their original toy or game inventions for a chance to win prizes and an opportunity to have their creations published.

headline: Homemade Baking Mix Brand, My Better Batch, Inks Distribution Deal With Target As It Expands National Footprint
summary: My Better Batch, the women-owned, better-for-you cookie mix brand reimagining what boxed baking can be, is proud to announce its newest retail launch with Target. Starting August 3, My Better Batch cookie mixes will officially roll out to Target stores across the country and online at Target.com, deepening the brand's national retail footprint and continuing a year of rapid growth.
